keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map \ passNextKey
map e passNextKey
map q passNextKey normal
map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map <c-b> scrollFullPageUp
map <c-f> scrollFullPageDown
map <a-h> goBack
map <a-l> goForward
